Notebook Features

Data Exploration:

  Loads a spam/ham email dataset

  Visualizes class distribution

Text Preprocessing:

  Removes punctuation and stopwords

  Applies stemming

  Uses TF-IDF for feature extraction

Model Training:

 Tests multiple algorithms:

   Naive Bayes

   Logistic Regression

   Random Forest

   SVM

  Evaluates using accuracy and cross-validation

Model Evaluation:

  Compares model performance

  Shows confusion matrix

  Displays ROC curve

  Prediction Pipeline:

  Creates an end-to-end pipeline

 Tests on sample emails

Saves the trained model
